          <button class="faq-cat" data-target="faq-g4"><svg class="faq-ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="6"/><path d="m15.477 12.89 1.515 8.526a.5.5 0 0 1-.81.47l-3.58-2.687a1 1 0 0 0-1.197 0l-3.586 2.686a.5.5 0 0 1-.81-.469l1.514-8.526"/></svg><span class="faq-cat-n">AMD Solution Award</span><span class="faq-cat-c">1</span></button>
          <button class="faq-cat" data-target="faq-g5"><svg class="faq-ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M7.9 20A9 9 0 1 0 4 16.1L2 22Z"/></svg><span class="faq-cat-n">联系与更新</span><span class="faq-cat-c">1</span></button>
        </nav>

        <div class="faq-cards">
          <section class="faq-card" id="faq-g1">
            <div class="faq-card-h"><svg class="faq-ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 3v18"/><path d="M5 4h13l-3 4 3 4H5z"/></svg><h2>入门</h2><span class="faq-card-c">4 个问题</span></div>
            <div class="faq-qa is-open"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="true"><span class="faq-q-t">如何报名？</span><svg class="faq-chev" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="faq-a"><p>在<a href="register.html">报名页</a>注册 1–6 人的团队。Member 1 为联系人，接收全部团队邮件。</p></div></div>
            <div class="faq-qa is-open"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="true"><span class="faq-q-t">是否涉及报名费？</span><svg class="faq-chev" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="faq-a"><p>不收费——参赛免费。</p></div></div>
            <div class="faq-qa is-open"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="true"><span class="faq-q-t">可以单人参赛吗？需要自己组队吗？</span><svg class="faq-chev" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="faq-a"><p>每队 1–6 人，允许单人参赛，且由你自行组队。找队友可用 <a href="https://discord.gg/pGwRbMRjuH" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Discord</a>，中国大陆参赛者可加入<a href="https://qr61.cn/oioUKl/qtksKk2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">上海测试平台微信群</a>。</p></div></div>
            <div class="faq-qa is-open"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="true"><span class="faq-q-t">需要什么经验水平？</span><svg class="faq-chev" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="faq-a"><p>欢迎各水平参与——我们提供 Baseline 示例与教程。</p></div></div>
          </section>

          <section class="faq-card" id="faq-g2">
            <div class="faq-card-h"><svg class="faq-ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9H4.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0-5H6"/><path d="M18 9h1.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 0-5H18"/><path d="M4 22h16"/><path d="M10 14.66V17c0 .55-.47.98-.97 1.21C7.85 18.75 7 20.24 7 22"/><path d="M14 14.66V17c0 .55.47.98.97 1.21C16.15 18.75 17 20.24 17 22"/><path d="M18 2H6v7a6 6 0 0 0 12 0V2Z"/></svg><h2>赛事</h2><span class="faq-card-c">6 个问题</span></div>
            <div class="faq-qa is-open"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="true"><span class="faq-q-t">有哪些赛题？</span><svg class="faq-chev" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="faq-a"><p>三个独立赛题——Task 1：Cable Routing &amp; Plugging；Task 2：Deformable Material Handling（Thermal Pad Placement）；Task 3：Assisted Living &amp; Feeding。可任选一个或多个，各赛题独立排名。</p></div></div>
            <div class="faq-qa is-open"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="true"><span class="faq-q-t">使用哪些仿真器？</span><svg class="faq-chev" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="faq-a"><p>NVIDIA Isaac Sim 与 MuJoCo。Task 2 的 MuJoCo 版本暂不随发布分发（可变形物体精度尚未达标）；如自行搭建仍然有效。</p></div></div>
            <div class="faq-qa is-open"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="true"><span class="faq-q-t">提供哪些遥操作接口？</span><svg class="faq-chev" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="faq-a"><p>Teleoperation Toolkit 提供 <a href="https://franka.de/de/gello" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Franka Duo GELLO</a>、键盘控制、脚踏板控制与 VR 控制。</p></div></div>
            <div class="faq-qa is-open"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="true"><span class="faq-q-t">需要出差或到现场吗？</span><svg class="faq-chev" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="faq-a"><p>赛事以仿真为主——开放仿真基准通过公开招募进行，无需出差。从仿真晋级的团队将在汉堡、慕尼黑、匹兹堡和上海的合作实验室，于真实的 Mobile FR3 Duo 机器人上进行真实世界验证，分为两个窗口：晋级团队在真实平台上的实操调试窗口（2026 年 8 月 10 日 – 8 月 19 日），随后为组织方运行的窗口（2026 年 8 月 20 日 – 8 月 31 日），团队可继续提交代码，所有真实机器人的台架测试与评估均由组织方运行，以确保跨站点可比性。</p></div></div>
            <div class="faq-qa is-open"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="true"><span class="faq-q-t">仿真包与 Baseline 何时发布？</span><svg class="faq-chev" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="faq-a"><p>首个公开版本即将发布：仿真环境、Teleoperation Toolkit、Benchmark 文档与 Baseline 示例。请关注 <a href="https://discord.gg/pGwRbMRjuH" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Discord</a> 与官网获取发布公告。</p></div></div>
            <div class="faq-qa is-open"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="true"><span class="faq-q-t">如何评测提交结果？</span><svg class="faq-chev" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="faq-a"><p>官方规则手册与评测指标将随 Benchmark 包一同发布；提交说明随后给出。</p></div></div>
